sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant App as Android App
    participant Firestore as Firestore DB
    participant HttpFunction as HTTP Trigger Function
    participant ScheduledFunction as Scheduled Function
    participant LLM as LLM Service (Gemini/OpenAI)
    participant Email as Email Service (Brevo)
    
    User->>App: Start App Session
    App->>Firestore: Store APP_SESSION_START Event<br>(applications/{id}/metadata/{eventId})
    App->>HttpFunction: Trigger Metadata Event (HTTP POST)
    Note over App: Include deviceInfo in payload
    
    User->>App: Navigate to Screen
    App->>Firestore: Store SCREEN_VISIT Event<br>(screenName, startTime)
    App->>HttpFunction: Trigger Screen Visit Event
    
    User->>App: Complete Form Section
    App->>Firestore: Store SECTION_COMPLETED Event<br>(screenName, sectionName, duration)
    App->>HttpFunction: Trigger Section Completion Event
    
    User->>App: Upload Document
    App->>Firestore: Store DOCUMENT_EVENT Event<br>(documentType, action, status)
    App->>HttpFunction: Trigger Document Event
    
    User->>App: Put App in Background
    App->>Firestore: Store APP_BACKGROUNDED Event
    App->>HttpFunction: Trigger APP_BACKGROUNDED Event
    
    HttpFunction->>ScheduledFunction: Schedule Drop-off Check (30s)
    Note over ScheduledFunction: After 30s, check for activity
    
    ScheduledFunction->>Firestore: Query for recent activity
    
    alt No Activity for >30 seconds
        ScheduledFunction->>Firestore: Check Application Status
        
        alt Status = IN_PROGRESS
            ScheduledFunction->>Firestore: Fetch Application Data
            ScheduledFunction->>Firestore: Fetch Recent Metadata Events
            ScheduledFunction->>+LLM: Send Drop-off Analysis Request
            Note over LLM: Analyze Data for Drop-off Patterns
            LLM-->>-ScheduledFunction: Drop-off Analysis (profile, rank, issues)
            
            ScheduledFunction->>Firestore: Update Status to DROPPED_OFF
            ScheduledFunction->>+Email: Send Drop-off Summary
            Email-->>-ScheduledFunction: Email Sent Confirmation
        end
    end
    
    alt User Returns Within Timeout
        User->>App: Bring App to Foreground
        App->>Firestore: Store APP_FOREGROUNDED Event
        App->>HttpFunction: Trigger APP_FOREGROUNDED Event
        Note over HttpFunction: Cancel pending Drop-off Check
    end
    
    Note over User,Email: Async Processing Flow Completed
